channel.title: Unfinished reflection bot
channel.description:
This is Reflect0r, a reflection bot base i made and i recently started working on again. This is the first 4 hours of work. It loads the field data from a text file that my updater dumped :). I also added an internal updater because i can't be fucked to work with reflection to get the canvas, and the next reason i did it is because we can now load signed applets which is <3.
Anyways, enjoy (src is included).
http://uppit.com/v/D2YJKXTY
